title: Create gizmo application
body:

There are multiple items we need to  complete for that:

title: Design Gizmo data model
body:
A gizmo has two fields as follow:
- [ ] foo
- [ ] bar

title: Create Gizmo back-end
body: We need to create a backend with a rest API

title: Create Gizmo front-end UI
body: We need to create a frontend with a web UI
